Package TranRunJLite

Interface Summary
TrjTime A time class for TranRunJLite that operates in real time.
 

Class Summary
BoxProfile Implement a "box" profile (constant derivative) This class extends the ProfileGenerator class so it only has to provide the missing functions.
CosineProfile Implement a "cosine" profile (S-shaped velocity profile with constant velocity cruise section) This class extends the ProfileGenerator class so it only has to provide the missing functions.
HysteresisControl Hysteresis Controller for single-input, single-output systems.
Jogger Implement a "Jogger," a task that will move an axis forward by integrating the specified velocity and feeding the resulting position to a feedback controller.
PIDControl PID controller for single-input, single-output systems.
ProfileGenerator Profile Generator -- an abstract class to support a variety of profile generation modes.
PWMGenerator  
SISOFeedback Base class for single-input, single-output feedback control.
TrapezoidProfile Implement a "trapezoid" profile (constant accel, constant derivative, constant decel) This class extends the ProfileGenerator class so it only has to provide the missing functions.
TrjState  
TrjSys TranRunJLite TrjSys class Implements a simple version of a task/state system.
TrjTask The task class.
TrjTimeAccel A time class for TranRunJLite that operates in accelerated realtime.
TrjTimeReal A time class for TranRunJLite that operates in real time.
TrjTimeSim A Simulation timer class that is based on TrjTime.
